:42.000Z","msg":"今朝MISS左......<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9426d49983dcbfbc704b9c5a4732ba9e7d89a097","tid":2507194,"uid":127568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"微軟上季多賺44%　收入升19%勝預期<br />\n<br />\n微軟上季盈利154.6億美元，按年升44%。每股經調整盈利1.95美元，高於預期的1.78美元。期內，收入417億美元，按年升19%，好過預期。雲計算產品Azure收入急升50%，包括Azure及企業服務等的「智能雲」業務收入151億美元，按年升23%，略高於市場預期。至於包括Azure等伺服器的「商業雲」業務收入177億美元，按年升33%。集團預計，本財年最後1季亦即今季，整體收入介乎436億至445億美元，「智能雲」業務收入介乎162億至164.5億美元。<br />\n<br />\n大戶想壓就壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c237eaf28069d4a7974309f59aec765b5471323e","tid":2507194,"uid":352740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:21:08.000Z","msg":"求240想入<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323a13d3a9fddabf8c6d128f753e048cf695c2f4","tid":2507194,"uid":65928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f43c512787aa091d359c032f00e0764f7b855e","tid":2507194,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"符合預期都跌咩意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"Intel 每個season都超預期<br />\n<br />\n差唔多每次都西冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/ball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4386201463b747b7efb4891e03130ee4c3dbba23","tid":2507194,"uid":127568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"323a13d3a9fddabf8c6d128f753e048cf695c2f4","tid":2507194,"uid":65928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f43c512787aa091d359c032f00e0764f7b855e","tid":2507194,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"符合預期都跌咩意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"Intel 每個season都超預期<br />\n<br />\n差唔多每次都西冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/ball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:31:58.000Z","msg":"佢壇生意咁多不確定性 冇得同我地廢老股咁比"}]}